s, buy &amp; sell in the student marketplace, find campus gigs, and connect with students across universities.\"/><meta name=\"application-name\" content=\"UniLoomy\"/><link rel=\"author\" href=\"https://uniloomy.com\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"UniLoomy Technologies Ltd\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><meta name=\"generator\" content=\"Next.js\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"UniLoomy,university app Ghana,student app Ghana,campus app,student marketplace Ghana,student gigs Ghana,study tools Ghana,UniClips,campus social app,Looms rewards,University of Ghana app,KNUST app,student housing Ghana,learn earn connect,Ghanaian student platform\"/><meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"origin-when-cross-origin\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"UniLoomy Technologies Ltd\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"UniLoomy Technologies Ltd\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><meta name=\"category\" content=\"Education, Social, Marketplace\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://uniloomy.com\"/><meta name=\"google-site-verification\" content=\"REPLACE_WITH_GOOGLE_SEARCH_CONSOLE_KEY\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"UniLoomy — Learn Smarter. Earn Bigger. Connect Deeper.\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Ghana&#x27;s all-in-one university super-app. Study smarter with AI tools, earn Looms rewards, use the student marketplace, find campus gigs, watch UniClips, and connect with students across universities.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://uniloomy.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"UniLoomy\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GH\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://uniloomy.com/og-image.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"UniLoomy — The Super App for University Students\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:site\" content=\"@uniloomy\"/><meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"@uniloomy\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"UniLoomy — Learn Smarter. Earn Bigger. Connect Deeper.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Ghana&#x27;s all-in-one university super-app. AI study tools, student marketplace, campus gigs, UniClips, Looms rewards, and more.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://uniloomy.com/og-image.png\"/><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/icon.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.png\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-icon.png\" type=\"image/png\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"UniLoomy\",\"url\":\"https://uniloomy.com\",\"logo\":\"https://uniloomy.com/icon.png\",\"description\":\"Ghana's all-in-one university super-app for learning, earning, and connecting.\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressCountry\":\"GH\"},\"sameAs\":[\"https://twitter.com/uniloomy\",\"https://linkedin.com/company/uniloomy\"]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"MobileApplication\",\"name\":\"UniLoomy\",\"operatingSystem\":\"iOS, Android\",\"applicationCategory\":\"EducationApplication\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"GHS\"},\"description\":\"UniLoomy is the all-in-one university super-app for Ghanaian students — AI study tools, marketplace, gigs, social feed, UniClips, and Looms rewards.\"}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><main class=\"relative min-h-screen grid-overlay flex flex-col pt-6 md:pt-10 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24\"><nav class=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto glass-dark px-5 md:px-10 py-4 md:py-5 rounded-full z-50 mb-6 md:mb-12 animate-fade-in shadow-glow\"><div class=\"flex items-center\"><img alt=\"UniLoomy Logo\" width=\"160\" height=\"44\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-8 w-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-10 text-white/50 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\"><a href=\"#features\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Ecosystem</a><a href=\"#how\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">How it Works</a><a href=\"#game\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Play &amp; Win</a><a href=\"#waitlist\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Early Access</a></div><button class=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-white rounded-xl text-primary font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 transition-transform active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-download w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 15V3\"></path><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><path d=\"m7 10 5 5 5-5\"></path></svg>Get App</button></nav><section class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-0 mt-2 md:mt-16 mb-20 md:mb-32\"><div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left gap-6 md:gap-8 md:pr-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-3 animate-fade-in\"><div class=\"pill bg-white text-primary md:-rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer\">Learn Smarter</div><div class=\"pill bg-primary text-white md:rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer\">Earn Bigger</div><div class=\"pill bg-primary-light text-white md:-rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer\">Connect Deeper</div></div><p class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-white leading-tight max-w-lg animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay:0.2s\">Your all-in-one platform designed for university students.</p><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm md:text-base max-w-md animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay:0.3s\">Learn, earn, and connect — not just with your campus, but with students from different universities and campuses across Ghana.</p><div id=\"waitlist\" class=\"w-full max-w-md animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay:0.4s\"><div class=\"w-full\"><form class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2\"><div class=\"relative flex-1\"><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"university-email@edu.gh\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-xl glass border border-white/5 text-white placeholder:text-slate-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary-light/50 transition-colors bg-white/[0.01]\" value=\"\"/></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary-light hover:text-white transition-all disabled:opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] active:scale-95\">Get Early Access<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg></button></form></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-4 animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay:0.5s\"><div class=\"flex -space-x-3 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"inline-block h-8 w-8 rounded-full ring-2 ring-primary-dark bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold\">A</div><div class=\"inline-block h-8 w-8 rounded-full ring-2 ring-primary-dark bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold\">B</div><div class=\"inline-block h-8 w-8 rounded-full ring-2 ring-primary-dark bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold\">C</div><div class=\"inline-block h-8 w-8 rounded-full ring-2 ring-primary-dark bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold\">D</div></div><div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center\">Join <span class=\"text-white mx-1\">thousands</span> of students on the waitlist</div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full flex justify-center md:justify-end animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay:0.4s\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[260px] md:max-w-[300px] aspect-[9/18.5] mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900 rounded-[3rem] border-8 border-slate-800 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden ring-4 ring-slate-800/50\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-6 bg-black rounded-full z-20\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white p-4 pt-12 flex flex-col gap-6 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-2\"><img alt=\"Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-5 w-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Funiloomy.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100\"></div><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\"><div class=\"w-20 h-2 bg-slate-200 rounded\"></div><div class=\"w-12 h-1.5 bg-slate-100 rounded\"></div></div></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"App Icon\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"opacity-20 grayscale\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Ficon.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Ficon.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Ficon.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"mt-auto flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-t border-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-slate-200 rounded\"></div><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-slate-100 rounded\"></div></div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-primary/30\"><div class=\"w-4 h-4 bg-white rounded-sm\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -right-6 top-1/4 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-light/20 blur-[2px] opacity-40 z-10\"></div><div class=\"absolute -left-8 bottom-1/3 w-16 h-16 rounded-[1rem] bg-primary-light/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 z-10\"></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto py-32 border-t border-white/5 relative\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10\"></div><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4\">One App. Your Entire Campus Life.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-bold text-xs\">Everything you need to own your university journey</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Learn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Smart Learning Hub</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Access AI-powered study tools, flashcards, practice tests, slides, pascos, and personalized learning paths to ace your courses.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Earn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Looms &amp; Rewards</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Earn Looms — our rewards points — for your academic contributions and community engagement. Real value for real effort.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shopping-bag w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0\"></path><path d=\"M3.103 6.034h17.794\"></path><path d=\"M3.4 5.467a2 2 0 0 0-.4 1.2V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6.667a2 2 0 0 0-.4-1.2l-2-2.667A2 2 0 0 0 17 2H7a2 2 0 0 0-1.6.8z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Earn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Student Marketplace</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">The student-exclusive economy. Buy, sell, and trade textbooks, gadgets, and more safely within your campus network.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-briefcase w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\"></path><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"6\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Earn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Campus Gigs</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Discover student gig opportunities to earn real income while you study. Tutoring, freelancing, and more — all within Uniloomy.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-tag w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.586 2.586A2 2 0 0 0 11.172 2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7.172a2 2 0 0 0 .586 1.414l8.704 8.704a2.426 2.426 0 0 0 3.42 0l6.58-6.58a2.426 2.426 0 0 0 0-3.42z\"></path><circle cx=\"7.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Earn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Exclusive Deals</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Unlock exclusive student discounts and deals from brands that care about university students and their financial wellbeing.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Social Feed &amp; Stories</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Connect with peers, share experiences, and explore what&#x27;s happening across different campuses in real-time.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Anonymous Discussions</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Speak freely. Share thoughts, seek advice, and engage in candid campus conversations without revealing your identity.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">UniClips</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Short-form video content created by and for university students. Learn, laugh, and share moments that define campus life.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-house w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8\"></path><path d=\"M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-6a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 6A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Student Housing</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Find verified, affordable student accommodation near your campus. No middlemen, no scams — just safe housing.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-newspaper w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 18h-5\"></path><path d=\"M18 14h-8\"></path><path d=\"M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect width=\"8\" height=\"4\" x=\"10\" y=\"6\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Campus News &amp; Events</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Stay up to date with campus news, upcoming events, concerts, and activities from your university and beyond.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-check w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16 11 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">All</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Verified Community</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">A safe, university-verified environment exclusively for students. Your campus identity, protected and authentic.</p></div><div class=\"glass-dark p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col gap-6 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group border-white/10 hover:border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trophy w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 1-.976 1.696A5 5 0 0 0 7 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M14 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 0 .976 1.696A5 5 0 0 1 17 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M18 9h1.5a1 1 0 0 0 0-5H18\"></path><path d=\"M4 22h16\"></path><path d=\"M6 9a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V3a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M6 9H4.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H6\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Learn</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">Study Groups &amp; Sessions</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Join or create study sessions, collaborate on assignments, and master your courses together with classmates.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"how\" class=\"w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto py-32 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-10 leading-tight\">Getting Started <br/>is <span class=\"text-primary-light italic\">Actually</span> Easy.</h2><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-12\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-white/10\">01</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Join the Waitlist</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium\">Sign up with your email to secure your spot. Early access members get exclusive Looms bonus points on launch.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-white/10\">02</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Verify Your Campus</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium\">Use your university email or student ID to join as a verified member of your campus community.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-white/10\">03</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Start Your Journey</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium\">Explore study tools, connect with peers, discover gigs, and start earning Looms from day one.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/10 rounded-[3rem] aspect-square flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5\"><div class=\"text-center p-12\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-graduation-cap w-24 h-24 text-primary-light mx-auto mb-6 animate-float\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z\"></path><path d=\"M22 10v6\"></path><path d=\"M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-white font-black text-2xl\">Launching at <br/> University of Ghana <br/> &amp; KNUST first.</p><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4 font-medium\">More universities coming soon.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"game\" class=\"w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto py-32 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><div class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-primary-light uppercase mb-6\">Interactive Campus Hub</div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4\">Earn Looms While You Wait</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400 font-medium\">UniLoomy Campus Runner — top scores earn early beta perks &amp; bonus Looms on launch day.</p></div><div class=\"w-full glass-dark p-10 rounded-[3rem] border-white/10 relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-[-10%] bottom-[-10%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full -z-10 animate-float-slow\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-24 h-24 bg-primary-light/10 blur-3xl rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl px-4\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-48 bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer group select-none transition-all hover:border-white/10\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-white/5 shadow-[0_-4px_10px_rgba(255,255,255,0.02)]\"></div><div class=\"absolute left-[50px] w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(77,111,255,0.2)] border border-white/10\" style=\"bottom:0\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-white/10\"></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-6 flex flex-col gap-0.5 z-10 pointer-events-none\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\">Score</span><span class=\"text-xl font-black text-white\">0</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-md flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-20 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"text-center mb-6\"><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-tight mb-1\">READY TO LOOM?</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">CLICK OR SPACE TO JUMP</p></div><button class=\"px-10 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:scale-105 transition-all flex items-center gap-3 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play w-3 h-3 fill-current\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\"></path></svg>Play Runner</button></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto py-40 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-10 tracking-tighter overflow-hidden\">Uni<span class=\"text-primary-light\">Loomy</span>.<br/>Your Campus <br/>Redefined.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed\">Join thousands of students already on the waitlist t